    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TaC4">
<l>ūḻitō ṟūḻi yōvātu vāḻiyē</l>
<l>yeṉṟi yāmtoḻa vicaiyuṅ kollō</l>
<l>yāvakai yulakamum yāvaru millā</l>
<l>mēlvarum perumpāḻk kālat tirumporuṭ</l>
<l>kellā marumpeṟal taṉivit torutā</l>
<l>ṉākit teyva nāṉmukak koḻumuḷai</l>
<l>yīṉṟu mukkaṇ ṇīcaṉoṭu tēvupala</l>
<l>nutalimū vulakam viḷaitta vunti</l>
<l>māyak kaṭavuḷ māmuta laṭiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>“May they live aeon after aeon, without end”,</l>
<l>will it be possible for us to worship thus</l>
<l>the feet of the great cause, the wonderous god</l>
<l>whose navel grew the three worlds, creating</l>
<l>many deities along with the three-eyed lord, bringing forth</l>
<l>the rich sprout with the [one of] divine four faces, being</l>
<l>the solitary one seed difficult to obtain of all</l>
<l>great matter at the time of the great destruction when</l>
<l>no kind of world and nobody come up.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
